    "All data analyses were conducted using IBM SPSS Statistics.",
    "Descriptive statistics were run and presented for all dependent variables (e.g., AI domains).",
    "Additional descriptive and reliability tests were run for all variables included in the analysis.",
    "Ordinary least squares regression models were then run to explore the relationships between individual traits and the extent to which they explained participants' comfort in AI managing various domains.",
    "Variables were entered step-wise into the models, in two blocks: (1) demographics and (2) individual traits."
